::Feline::

She went running along through the dence undergrowth.  She felt like herold 
self again.  She came to a small pod which appeared to have been there for a 
long time. She looked around, but didn't smell any other bots near by.  She 
tranformed into bot mode and checked out the pod.  She smiled and wondered 
if it was the answer to her situation. "Perhaps I can use this to fix up my 
little cruiser."  She opened up a panel and stuck her hand inside, trying to 
find the release mechanism for the propulsion ciruits.  She pulled her hand 
back as she felt something sharp puncture her skin.  She saw a strange 
spider biting her arm.  "Get off me you little insect."(yes I know a spider 
is an arachnid and not an insect)
She threw it to the ground and stepped on it, crushing it under her foot.  
She sneered at the pod. "I'll not touch that thing again if it's going to 
bite me back like that."
With that, she transformed into leopard mode and continued on her way.
